body:
Version 2.1.1

Framework:

- [Fix] BUG-10089 Crash when unloading plugin while automating a parameter
- [Fix] Warning dialog and broken UI in certain hosts if host alters
        the locale to something that uses , as decimal point instead of .

JE8086:

- [Imp] Patch Manager: Add support for .pat/.pfm preset files

- [Fix] BUG-10098 Automation parameters not updating when selecting a
        different patch/performance
- [Fix] Support Patch/Performance Dumps from edit buffers
- [Fix] Patch Manager list might erratically jump when selecting a Performance
- [Fix] Test Console: Fix name of binary and add missing macOS setup script

OsTIrus:

- [Fix] BUG-10083 Mode and Type labels were reversed for Delay on FX 2 page
- [Imp] BUG-10100 Patch Manager: Add support for .tfx presets from TDM plugin

Osirus:

- [Fix] BUG-10075 swap labels Slot 1 and Slot 3 [Hoverland/Galaxpel skins]
- [Fix] BUG-10106 Galaxpel skin: LFO link buttons had no effect
- [Fix] BUG-10106 Galaxpel skin: Add Pure Tuning parameter to global page
- [Fix] BUG-10106 Galaxpel skin: Fix inverted LFO Env Mode and Poly/Mono buttons
- [Imp] BUG-10100 Patch Manager: Add support for .tfx presets from TDM plugin

Xenia:

- [Fix] BUG-10057 BP Filter Offset din't display bipolar but unipolar values
- [Fix] BUG-10108 Crash when dragging a wave in the wave editor
